snippet.textDisplay:
I've listened to this man pour his god damn soul into every second, every beat, every word of EVERYTHING he has put out here for us to (hopefully) hear.
Not just to "hear the next catchy beat" he throws at us, but to actually fucking LISTEN to the words he has been spitting for SO long. I can't honestly think of but a tiny handful of artists these days that bleed The amount of passion into their music, like tom macdonald does consistently, enough to make the masses really fucking think about what the hell is coming out of their mouths...
Enough to feel what they feel, to the best of our understanding and our capacity.
You don't have to like this genre. You don't have to like Tom Macdonald. You don't have to like his fans or even those artists he collaborates with. No one fucking cares about the constant negative shit anyone has to say.
Honestly, regardless of your opinion on everything i just listed, you should at least be open minded enough to hear what this man has to say... He speaks the truth about a lot more shit than most any artist, too scared to even start looking for their own balls to grab onto... just so they could say the shit that Tom does.
